---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Cat Gear Index.">
  <article class="article-shell">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">This starter privacy policy must be reviewed before launch and updated for the analytics, advertising, affiliate, and email tools you actually use.</p>
    <h2>Information We May Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect standard analytics information such as pages viewed, device type, approximate location, referring pages, and interaction events.</p>
    <h2>Advertising and Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>If advertising or affiliate programs are enabled, third parties may use cookies or similar technologies to measure performance and personalize or limit ads according to their policies.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy questions, replace this sentence with a working contact email before public launch.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
